PORT : 5000

//patient interface 

Patient login - /api/patient/login : post , body - {mail,password}
Patient signup - /api/patient/signup : post body-{mail, name, password}
to get patient profile - /api/patient/profile :get , add token in the header
to update patient profile - /api/patient/profile :put ,add token in header and body -{mail, name}
to get patient report from patient interface -/api/patient/p_getreport :get , add token in the header
to upload report from the user interface -/api/patient/p_uploadFiles :post ,add token in the header and send uploaded file as file , refer /backend/middleware/filemiddleware.js
for ai chatbot -/api/patient/ask :post ,add token in the header and Body-{question}
to get the docters those who access that patient details - /api/patient/getdocters -get, add token in the header
to add docter -/api/patient/adddocter -post , add token in the header and Body:{docter_id}
to remove docter -/api/patient/removedocter -post , add token in header and Body:{docter_id}


//Docter interface

Docter login - /api/docter/login : post ,Body - {docter_id, password}
Docter signup - /api/docter/signup : post, Body - {docter_id, password, name, specialization, hospital }
to get docter profile -/api/docter/profile : get ,add token in the header
to update docter profile - /api/docter/profile : put ,add token in the header and Body -{name,specialization,hospital}
to get patient report from docter's interface - /api/docter/getrecords/:patient_id : get, add token in the header
to uplod patient's file from docter interface - api/docter/uploadrecord/:patient_id :post , add token in the header and inlcude file as a file ref the middleware
to get the patients being handled by that docter -api/docter/mypatients :get , add token in the header
